Instructions
- Use exact version ranges (`^`) for all dependencies.
- Do not include `postcss` or `autoprefixer` — Tailwind v4 uses CSS-first configuration without these.
- Do not include `tailwind.config.js` or related config — Tailwind v4 uses `@import "tailwindcss"` in globals.css.

Deliverable
- `package.json` — complete Node.js package manifest with all required deps and scripts.

Implementation assumptions (explicit)
- The project uses Next.js App Router (not Pages Router).
- Remotion rendering is done server-side via `@remotion/renderer` (not CLI).
- Python subprocess scripts (render_tts.py, sync_audio_pipeline.py, generate_section_compositions.py) are invoked by the server via `child_process.spawn` — no Python Node.js bindings needed.

Please produce a complete, correct package.json consistent with the above.
